2. Luo, Y., & Mesgarani, N. (2018). **TasNet: Time-Domain Audio Separation Network for Real-Time, Single-Channel Speech Separation**. *ICASSP 2018*. [arXiv:1711.00541](https://arxiv.org/abs/1711.00541)
